              I first got introduced to programming in 2020. I was 6 back then. I learnt the basics, like HTML.
            </p>
            <p class="animate font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">
              2023
            </p>
            <p class="animate">
              During this time, I got introduced to Scratch in school.
            </p>
            <p class="animate font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">
              {year}
            </p>
            <p class="animate">
              Now.
            </p>
          </span>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
